00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:07.894
Namaskar!
Welcome to Nishamadhulika.com

00:00:08.371 --> 00:00:12.097
Today we are going to make milk powder coconut burfi.

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:17.389
This burfi is very tasty and is made easily.

00:00:17.707 --> 00:00:22.045
So come, let's prepare milk powder coconut burfi.

00:00:22.363 --> 00:00:34.729
Milk powder - 1 cup or 135 grams (Non fat)

00:00:35.339 --> 00:00:46.363
Desicated Coconut - 1 cup or 80 gram 
This is easily available in the market.

00:00:46.688 --> 00:00:53.958
Powdered sugar - 3/4 cup or 125 grams

00:00:54.442 --> 00:00:56.743
Milk - 3/4 cup

00:00:57.188 --> 00:00:59.658
Green cardamom (Chhoti elaichi) - 6 to 7

00:00:59.817 --> 00:01:01.410
Pistachios (Pista) - 10 to 12

00:01:01.657 --> 00:01:09.323
Unsalted butter - 1/4 cup or 50 grams

00:01:09.776 --> 00:01:19.426
To prepare the burfi, first we'll cut the pistachios into tiny pieces.

00:01:20.141 --> 00:01:26.607
Now peel the green cardamom and make a powder.

00:01:28.044 --> 00:01:32.885
We have made a powder of green cardamom.

00:01:33.133 --> 00:01:42.029
Add butter to the pan and let it melt.

00:01:42.307 --> 00:01:46.909
Once the butter is melted, add milk to it.

00:01:47.498 --> 00:01:49.678
Cook it on low flame.

00:01:49.871 --> 00:01:51.156
Mix everything well.

00:01:51.442 --> 00:01:54.601
Now add milk powder to it.

00:01:55.768 --> 00:01:58.013
Add little milk powder and make sure to keep mixing.

00:01:58.371 --> 00:02:09.096
Turn off the gas when mixing.

00:02:10.133 --> 00:02:20.645
Keep stirring till the milk powder and butter are completely
mixed and no bubbles remain. Make sure to cook it on low flame.

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:25.580
Keep mixing and mash it completely.

00:02:28.220 --> 00:02:33.082
Our milk powder is now completely mixed in milk.

00:02:33.736 --> 00:02:39.550
Keep mixing and cook it for some more time.

00:02:39.757 --> 00:02:44.863
Now add powdered sugar as well.

00:02:46.101 --> 00:02:53.023
Keep mixing it this way.

00:02:54.039 --> 00:03:03.399
Our mixture is now quite thick, so let's add powdered coconut as well.

00:03:03.585 --> 00:03:05.529
Add cardamom powder as well.

00:03:06.069 --> 00:03:10.436
Mix everything well and cook till it becomes thick.

00:03:10.849 --> 00:03:23.728
Make sure to cook it on medium or low flame so
that it does not stick to the bottom of the pan.

00:03:24.180 --> 00:03:28.123
Mix it this way and let it become thick.

00:03:28.639 --> 00:03:45.361
The mixture has now become of a freezing
consistency, so now let's freeze it in a plate.

00:03:45.974 --> 00:03:47.370
Turn off the flame.

00:03:47.855 --> 00:03:57.556
Apply a little ghee on the plate in which we are going to freeze the burfi and then spread it evenly on all sides.

00:04:01.387 --> 00:04:03.283
We have applied oil on the plate this way.

00:04:04.990 --> 00:04:07.839
Pour the mixture on the plate.

00:04:13.752 --> 00:04:19.650
Spread the mixture evenly this way.

00:04:21.857 --> 00:04:30.855
Apply a little oil on the spoon and use it to spread the burfi.

00:04:31.506 --> 00:04:34.691
Our burfi is now smooth.

00:04:34.969 --> 00:04:43.997
Sprinkle pistachios on the top and press it
with a spoon so that they set inside the burfi.

00:04:45.244 --> 00:04:46.839
Press it with a spoon like this.

00:04:48.935 --> 00:04:58.659
Now let's freeze the burfi, then we will cut it into pieces.

00:04:59.133 --> 00:05:00.966
So let's freez.

00:05:01.427 --> 00:05:05.359
Our milk powder coconut burfi is now frozen.

00:05:05.614 --> 00:05:07.878
It took about 1 hour to freeze the burfi.

00:05:08.307 --> 00:05:13.891
Now cut it into pieces as per your choice.

00:05:21.553 --> 00:05:31.175
Put the plate over the flame so that the burfi comes out easily.

00:05:31.231 --> 00:05:42.682
Heat the plate a little this way.

00:05:43.347 --> 00:05:47.569
Take out the burfi pieces and put it in the plate.

00:05:51.601 --> 00:06:00.393
Take out the burfi pieces this way and put it in a plate.

00:06:13.553 --> 00:06:17.132
Milk powder coconut burfi is now ready.

00:06:17.450 --> 00:06:22.331
Very tasty burfi is prepared and it is made very easily.

00:06:23.109 --> 00:06:30.812
Everything needs to be mixed properly till it has
a thick consistency and then needs to be frozen.

00:06:31.027 --> 00:06:34.392
Milk powder coconut burfi will be ready.

00:06:34.622 --> 00:06:40.166
You can enjoy eating milk powder coconut burfi
for about 7 days if stored in the refrigerator.

00:06:41.142 --> 00:06:45.545
You can also eat this burfi during fasting.

